{
  "texts": [
    "Specifically, for abstracting the behaviour of loops, verifiers aim at computing loop invariants.",
    "Our first step in evaluating ChatGPT's usefulness for software verification is thus the generation of loop invariants.To this end, we ask ChatGPT to annotate C-programs with loop invariants.",
    "We have chosen 106 C-programs from the Loops category of the annual competition on software verification [7].",
    "To enable the usage of these invariants by verifiers, we needed the invariants to be given in some formal language.",
    "For this, we have chosen ANSI/ISO C Specification Language (ACSL) [5], a designby-contract like annotation language for C. Initial experiments confirmed that ChatGPT \"knows\" ACSL."
  ]
}